data.description: Welcome to Laurel Woods Estates!  Situated on a fenced .46 acre lot, this home includes a patio, garden area, firepit, storage shed and an above-ground pool for backyard entertainment and lots of room for your furry friends. This community conveniently located right off Caratoke Hwy in Currituck includes walking trails, a dog run, playgrounds and RV storage.  Downstairs you will find a separate living room off the foyer before you enter into the main living area with an open, updated kitchen and family room.  There is a dining room currently used as a bar, which conveys with the home.  Upstairs are four spacious rooms.  The primary bedroom features a walk-in closet and large bathroom with a separate soaking tub and dual vanity.  Check out the virtual tour.  You will feel right at home! Only 15 minutes to Moyock, 20 minutes to the Virginia border and 30 minutes to the Wright Memorial Bridge headed to the Outer Banks!  Possible Assumable VA loan at 2.25% interest rate
